 6ï¸âƒ£ Public Endpoint vs Private Endpoint

Public Endpoint:
â†’ Internet required
â†’ Public IP / NAT / IGW
â†’ Less secure

Private Endpoint (VPC Endpoint):
â†’ No internet
â†’ Private IP only
â†’ High security

