 7ï¸âƒ£ VPC Peering

What it is:
Two VPCs ke beech private network connection

Important points:
â†’ One-to-one connection
â†’ Transitive nahi hota
â†’ Same region ya cross-region possible
â†’ Private IPs use hote hain

How it works:
â†’ Peering request accept karna hota hai
â†’ Route table me entries add karni hoti hain
â†’ Security group allow rules

Cost:
â†’ Peering connection free
â†’ Data transfer chargeable

AWS Example:
â†’ VPC-A (App servers)
â†’ VPC-B (Database)
â†’ Private traffic between them

Industry use:
â†’ Multi-team architecture
â†’ Prod & Dev separation
â†’ Shared services VPC

