â†’ Traffic kaha jayega
â†’ IGW
â†’ NAT
â†’ VGW
â†’ VPC Peering
â†’ VPC Endpoint

Without route table entry:
â†’ Connection kaam nahi karega
â†’ Even agar resource exist karta ho

